func vmnet_network_configuration_set_ipv6_prefix(

## [ Parameters ](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_ipv6_prefix(_:_:_:)#parameters)

`config`The network configuration object to be modified.

`prefix`The IPv6 prefix.

`len`The IPv6 prefix length.

## [Return Value](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_ipv6_prefix(_:_:_:)#return-value)

VMNET_SUCCESS on success, error otherwise.

## [Discussion](/documentation/vmnet/vmnet_network_configuration_set_ipv6_prefix(_:_:_:)#discussion)

Configures the IPv6 prefix for a vmnet network object.
